icID=520.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   What new AAs would you like to see??</span><hr size=1> Myself, I'd like to see the following AAs:<br>
<br>
(Archtype) Expanded Intellect: Increase your natural mana pool by 2, 5, and 10%.   Cost: 2/4/6<br>
<br>
(Class) Summoned Focusing: All pets summoned by the mage will recieve the benefit of being 1 level higher, thus benefiting from greater damage, higher skills, and higher hps.  Cost: 6<br>
<br>
(Class) Elemental Combat Fury: Through increased training and control your pets are able to land more prescise attacks on an opponent giving a 2, 4, and 7% chance for critical hits thru pets.  Cost: 3/6/9<br>
<br>
Just some ideas I came up with.<br>
<br>
